{"tid":578961,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"八婆親戚想介紹個成二百磅既肥仔俾我識..","createTime":"2018-03-03T06:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T03:08:00.000Z","uid":82845,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"561856a1d3b0792158372a8edc906a2b17b9c0a2","tid":578961,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:59:08.000Z","msg":"過年最煩既就係遇著D八婆親戚,<br />\n今年我就非常唔好彩咁中咗招,<br />\n話說個日去我舅父屋企拜年,<br />\n食飯個陣我舅母問我有冇男朋友,我話啱啱分咗手...<br />\n佢就話要介紹男仔俾我識,<br />\n如果係靚仔我都覺得OK啊,<br />\n點知佢話想介紹個成二百磅既肥仔俾我識,<br />\n話係佢朋友個仔,同我一樣咁鐘意食,仲話同我企埋一齊肯定好襯??<br />\nWhat the ???我自問個樣都唔差,雖然呢兩年多咗個肚腩,但都唔至於同個肥仔襯掛?<br />\n新年流流又唔好意思即場反面,唯有扮曬客氣咁同舅母話唔洗咁麻煩,佢仲係咁sell個肥仔有幾好,真係聽到都覺得煩!!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=758214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.beautyexchange.com.hk%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D758214&d=%2Fj%2FDjIROJYT7MDUWTicArb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=da12bf63\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=758214</a>"},{"pid":"29629c366408032a358397695d6314b40b70ede7","tid":578961,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"肥仔都可以係優質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肥可以減架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">樣衰另計</span></span>"},{"pid":"5a33a2963e295ea8b426bf925ae7aa184cb1137e","tid":578961,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"女人有肚腩應該好撚肥"},{"pid":"ba4dc0a56fe065285294841c31852ba1fb430e18","tid":578961,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T09:20:28.000Z","msg":"同我拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你就唔洗擔心個肥仔"},{"pid":"f27716bfd9a334e120cdaaabd035d0cd09646ba7","tid":578961,"uid":61398,"like":2,"di